<h2>Spots on throat, Spots on tonsils, Swollen tonsils and White patches inside mouth</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms spots on throat, spots on tonsils, swollen tonsils and white patches inside mouth including Tonsillitis, Viral pharyngitis, and Scarlet fever.</p>
<p>There  are 6 conditions  associated with spots on throat, spots on tonsils, swollen tonsils and white patches inside mouth. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
